{
  "_comment": "Consumer-side cockpit view of selfdef SDD-081 hot-store retention. Renders the daemon's /metrics retention series: enabled gauge, pruned-rate, cumulative sweeps + pruned, and live hot-store size. Pairs with the SelfdefStoreRetentionStalled alert (config/prometheus/alerts/selfdef-store-retention.rules.yml).",
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
